    "name": "Man I Just Wanna Go Home",
    "steam_appid": 3010070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In an unfamiliar part of the city</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/d4a2b370e1294ec63e18cad037987049.gif?t=1762338011\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/d4a2b370e1294ec63e18cad037987049.poster.avif?t=1762338011\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Under the devastating rain</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/829eae6c15bf646af9af34ebc41d1190.gif?t=1762338011\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/829eae6c15bf646af9af34ebc41d1190.poster.avif?t=1762338011\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You, a delivery person, are stranded with a dead cellphone, a couple of coins, no means of transportation and absolutely zero idea what to do next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the word on the street is - there's a murderer on the loose</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/0ba5a884d29d6d13b62fb7f4706217f2.avif?t=1762338011\" width=616 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The only thing you need is to GET HOME.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This visual novel offers you:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 13 unique endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Choose your own adventure&quot; gameplay in which every choice matters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Atmospheric visuals drawn in MS Paint </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A killer 80s style synth soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A charming roster of characters to meet, to talk to and die with</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A multilayered puzzle of a narrative  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to kick a cop</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam capsule by Artyom Trakhanov</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chinese translation by Cencil</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Japanese translation by Jun Kurihara</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/d80c978f95f810e1ff2b1ae714e662d3.apng?t=1762338011\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/d80c978f95f810e1ff2b1ae714e662d3.poster.avif?t=1762338011\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=347 /></picture></span></p>",
